OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be dry with
OL,8,Flengthy clear periods. Chance of a
OL,9,Fground frost in sheltered glens.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,12,Fday with plenty of sunshine, some high
OL,13,Fcloud in the afternoon. Winds light.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,16,Fdry and settled few days with plenty
OL,17,Fof sunshine, feeling quite warm.
OL,18,FPatchy overnight frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
